sequenceDiagram
    participant S as server.js
    participant ENV as envManager
    participant CFG as ConfigService
    participant MIG as MigrationService
    participant HC as HealthCheck
    participant VS as VoiceService
    participant PTS as PrayerTimeService
    participant AAS as AudioAssetService
    participant AMIG as AssetMigrationService
    participant SCH as SchedulerService

    S->>ENV: Load .env · Generate JWT_SECRET if absent
    S->>CFG: init()
    activate CFG
    CFG->>CFG: Merge default.json + local.json
    CFG->>MIG: migrateConfig() — V1→V2→V3→V4→V5
    CFG->>MIG: migrateEnvSecrets() — first-boot secret migration
    CFG->>CFG: Zod validate merged config
    deactivate CFG

    S->>HC: runStartupChecks()
    activate HC
    HC->>HC: API self-test (localhost:3000/api/health)
    HC->>HC: TTS ping (localhost:8000/health)
    deactivate HC

    S->>VS: init() — Fetch + cache available TTS voices

    S->>PTS: refreshCache()
    activate PTS
    PTS->>PTS: Fetch current year prayer data
    PTS->>PTS: Fetch next year prayer data
    deactivate PTS

    S->>AAS: syncAudioAssets() — Validate sidecar metadata · generate missing TTS
    S->>AMIG: run() — Legacy audio file migrations

    S->>SCH: initScheduler()
    activate SCH
    SCH->>SCH: Schedule all prayer events via node-schedule
    SCH->>SCH: Schedule midnight refresh job
    SCH->>SCH: Schedule stale-data check job
    deactivate SCH

    Note over S: Express server listening on :3000